OL,5,G0100 Outback Truckers
OL,6,     FIt's mid-afternoon in Perth and
OL,7,     FDion's super size convoy is
OL,8,     Fpushing hard to get out of the
OL,9,     Fcity before sunset. And the fate
OL,10,     Fof Steve's trip hangs on one phone
OL,11,     Fcall to his mechanic.
OL,12,G0200 Trucking Heavy
OL,13,     FThe action-packed series that
OL,14,     Ffollows men and women working in
OL,15,     Fthe heavy recovery business,
OL,16,     Ftackling jack-knifed lorries,
OL,17,     Fcrashed HGVs and roadside
OL,18,     Fbreakdowns.
